WEBVTT

00:01.470 --> 00:02.840
It’s good to be ordinary.

00:02.840 --> 00:05.410
People won’t look at you funny if you’re ordinary.

00:06.010 --> 00:09.340
I don’t understand the feelings of people who want to stand out.

00:09.930 --> 00:13.680
I don’t have the confidence to want to stand out.

00:14.490 --> 00:19.080
But is it because I’ve become ordinary that Mom and Dad don’t pay attention to me?

00:19.730 --> 00:21.480
Misato-chan is different.

00:22.050 --> 00:24.160
She’s a friend of ordinary me.
